OL,3,CEaster staycations spike as people
OL,4,Cstay closer to home in 'uncertain
OL,5,Ctimes'
OL,7,FLast-minute Easter staycations surged
OL,8,Fthis year as more people opted for
OL,9,Ftrips closer to home amid turbulence
OL,10,Foverseas and worries over renewed cost-
OL,11,Fof-living pressures, new figures show.
OL,13,FRecent bookings data suggests that
OL,14,Ftrips within the UK have become more
OL,15,Fpopular in light of conflict in the
OL,16,FMiddle East.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
