OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775617413
OL,3,CEaster staycations spike as people
OL,4,Cstay closer to home in 'uncertain
OL,5,Ctimes'
OL,7,FAwaze, which is Europe's biggest
OL,8,Fholiday homes business, said next-day
OL,9,Fbookings spiked by a third over the
OL,10,Ftwo weeks leading up to Easter,
OL,11,Fcompared with the same period a year
OL,12,Fago.
OL,14,FThis trend continued for trips into
OL,15,Fthe Easter weekend with bookings made
OL,16,Fin the week ahead surging by 38% for
OL,17,FUK getaway brands Cottages.com and by
OL,18,F11% for Hoseasons.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
