OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775617413
OL,3,CEaster staycations spike as people
OL,4,Cstay closer to home in 'uncertain
OL,5,Ctimes'
OL,7,FDemand was being led by coastal
OL,8,Fdestinations including Cornwall, Devon
OL,9,Fand Norfolk and countryside spots such
OL,10,Fas Yorkshire and Cumbria, amid sunnier
OL,11,Fweather sweeping across the country.
OL,13,FAwaze said that more than a fifth of
OL,14,Fall UK bookings are now made within
OL,15,Ftwo weeks of departure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
