OL,3,CEaster staycations spike as people
OL,4,Cstay closer to home in 'uncertain
OL,5,Ctimes'
OL,7,FMeanwhile, holiday parks provider
OL,8,FParkdean Resorts said an uptick in
OL,9,Fsearches for British coastal
OL,10,Fdestinations has seen the likes of
OL,11,FMorecambe Bay in Lancashire and Dover
OL,12,Fin Kent in high demand over the past
OL,13,Fweek as holidaymakers look to stay
OL,14,Fcloser to home.
OL,16,FLast week, travel agent Lastminute.com
OL,17,Frevealed that the war in the Middle
OL,18,FEast had affected around 17,000
OL,19,Fbookings, due to airspace closures in
OL,20,Fthe region and the impact to consumer
OL,21,Fsentiment around travel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
