PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775617413
OL,3,CEaster staycations spike as people
OL,4,Cstay closer to home in 'uncertain
OL,5,Ctimes'
OL,7,FThe bookings platform said consumers
OL,8,Fhave been seeking reassurance and
OL,9,Fflexibility, and noted increased
OL,10,Fdemand for alternative holiday
OL,11,Fdestinations such as European city
OL,12,Fbreaks.
OL,14,FIt comes as the Foreign Office has
OL,15,Fissued new travel advice for a number
OL,16,Fof countries since the escalation of
OL,17,Fthe US-Israel war with Iran, and is
OL,18,Fcontinuing to advise against all but
OL,19,Fessential travel to places including
OL,20,Fthe United Arab Emirates and Qatar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775617413
OL,3,CEaster staycations spike as people
OL,4,Cstay closer to home in 'uncertain
OL,5,Ctimes'
OL,7,FMeanwhile, expectations for UK
OL,8,Finflation have worsened with many
OL,9,Feconomists forecasting a bounce this
OL,10,Fyear as higher fuel and energy costs
OL,11,Fpush up prices for households and
OL,12,Fbusinesses.
OL,14,FAwaze chief executive Matthew Price
OL,15,Fsaid: "In a period of geopolitical
OL,16,Funcertainty and with cost-of-living
OL,17,Fpressures not abating, we saw a huge
OL,18,Fspike in demand for staycations this
OL,19,FEaster across the country.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
