OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775617413
OL,3,CEaster staycations spike as people
OL,4,Cstay closer to home in 'uncertain
OL,5,Ctimes'
OL,7,F"The reality is in uncertain times,
OL,8,Fpeople don't stop prioritising
OL,9,Fholidays ` they look for options that
OL,10,Foffer an escape and feel effortless."
OL,12,FHe added that it is also reflective of
OL,13,Fa "more long-term shift in consumer
OL,14,Fbehaviour" with people preferring the
OL,15,Fcertainty and flexibility of UK
OL,16,Fstaycations without contending with
OL,17,F"unexpected changes out of their
OL,18,Fcontrol".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@eO]uD@COUvD@JO]yD@AOUzD@HO]
